projectfu.game-master.Item.SSfB2SP3DVfwslhv]{Breath} @ICON[offensive]</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">5</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">One creature</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p>You deal <strong>【HR + 15】</strong> <strong>(choose type)</strong> damage to the target.</p><p></p><table style=\"height:34px;width:100%;border-width:1px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p><strong>Spell</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.game-master.Item.rEWv1yWQHse3soqn]{Curse} @ICON[offensive]</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">5 × T</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">One creature</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">Scene</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p>The target suffers (<strong>choose one: dazed, shaken, slow, weak</strong>).</p><p></p><table style=\"height:34px;width:100%;border-width:1px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p><strong>Spell</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.game-master.Item.S291phTQNL0qbGYa]{Curse XL} @ICON[offensive]</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">10</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">One creature</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p>The target suffers (<strong>choose two: dazed, shaken, slow, weak</strong>).</p><p></p><table style=\"height:34px;width:100%;border-width:1px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p><strong>Spell</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.game-master.Item.e5IBMtSXDyfWo0kb]{Cursed Breath} @ICON[offensive]</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">10</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">One creature</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p>You deal <strong>【HR + 15】</strong> <strong>(choose type)</strong> damage to the target, and the target suffers <strong>(choose one: dazed, shaken, slow, weak)</strong>.</p><p></p><table style=\"height:34px;width:100%;border-width:1px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p><strong>Spell</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.game-master.Item.32sA6nb1MVPzP8lc]{Devastation}</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">30</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">Special</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p>You deal 30 <strong>(choose type)</strong> damage to every enemy you can see.</p><p>This spell should only be given to <strong>champion</strong> and <strong>elite</strong> enemies of <strong>level 30 or higher</strong>, which should only cast it once per turn during <strong>their last turn of the round</strong> (this creates a predictable pattern that Players can anticipate).</p><p></p><table style=\"height:34px;width:100%;border-width:1px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p><strong>Spell</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.game-master.Item.Up14pnEa8pWzGkDD]{Lick Wounds}</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">5</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">Self</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p>You recover 20 Hit Points.</p><p>This amount increases to 30 Hit Points if you are <strong>level 20 or higher</strong>, to 40 Hit Points if you are <strong>level 40 or higher</strong>, or to 50 Hit Points if you are <strong>level 60</strong> or higher.</p><p></p><table style=\"height:34px;width:100%;border-width:1px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p><strong>Spell</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.game-master.Item.MEp2lJPOwnmHvDwk]{Life Theft} @ICON[offensive]</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">10</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">One creature</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p>You deal <strong>【HR + 15】</strong> <strong>(choose type)</strong> damage to the target. Then, you recover an amount of Hit Points equal to half the Hit Point loss they suffered.</p><p></p><table style=\"height:34px;width:100%;border-width:1px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p><strong>Spell</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.game-master.Item.Jr3T9bVRZdWMmAIw]{Mind Theft} @ICON[offensive]</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">10</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">One creature</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p>You deal <strong>【HR + 15】</strong> <strong>(choose type)</strong> damage to the target. Then, you recover an amount of Mind Points equal to half the Hit Point loss they suffered.</p><p></p><table style=\"height:34px;width:100%;border-width:1px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p><strong>Spell</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.game-master.Item.PYXh4QmqJDiA2tqy]{Poison} @ICON[offensive]</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">10 × T</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">Up to three creatures</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p>Each target hit by this spell suffers <strong>poisoned</strong>.</p><p></p><table style=\"height:34px;width:100%;border-width:1px;margin-left:auto;margin-right:auto\" border=\"1\"><tbody><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p><strong>Spell</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>MP</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Target</strong></p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\"><strong>Duration</strong></p></td></tr><tr style=\"height:17px\"><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:33%\"><p>@UUID[Compendium.projectfu.game-master.Item.w93PJbDwQ2WvkXvK]{Quicken}</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:15%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">20</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">One creature</p></td><td style=\"height:17px;border-width:1px;width:26%\"><p style=\"text-align:center\">Instantaneous</p></td></tr></tbody></table><p></p><p>The target may perform a <strong>free attack</strong> with a weapon they have equipped (or with a <strong>basic attack</strong>, if the target is an NPC).</p><p></p><table style=\"height:34px;width:100%;border-width:1px;margin-left:auto;margin-rig